AllMusic Review by Jason Ankeny:

The music of the late pop vocalist Nancy LaMott is recalled in this posthumously-compiled collection of studio recordings, demos and unreleased songs. Included are "Too Late Now", "The Promise", "Another Mr. Right", "Your Love", "We Live On Borrowed Time" and the title cut.
